title: Jimmy Kimmel taunts ‘loyal viewer’ Trump for making him one of Google’s top trending people
description: Jimmy Kimmel thanked President Donald Trump's frequent criticism for boosting his visibility and making him Google's third most searched person globally in 2025.
content:
Late-night host Jimmy Kimmel thanked President Donald Trump on Thursday night for making him one of the top trending people on Google.
